"Complete fish farm management software built in Norway. Monitor water "
"chemistry, manage feeding schedules, track batches, and run AI-powered "
"dosing — all from a single dashboard. Designed for RAS, flow-through, and "
"open-pen aquaculture."
msgstr ""
"Komplett programvare for fiskeoppdrettsstyring bygget i Norge. Overvåk "
"vannkjemi, administrer fôringsplaner, spor partier og kjør AI-drevet "
"dosering — alt fra ett dashbord. Designet for RAS, gjennomstrømning og åpent"
" merd-oppdrett."

