"EC/pH-overvåking og vekststadiesporing — med 24+ forhåndsinnstilte "
"næringsformler klare til bruk."

msgid ""
"Managing a modern fish farm means tracking dozens of variables in real time "
"— dissolved oxygen, pH, ammonia, temperature, feed conversion ratios, and "
"mortality rates. Suderra's aquaculture software platform connects to every "
"sensor on your facility and unifies all data into one system."
