msgid ""
"Suderra AS is a vertically integrated aquaculture technology company "
"headquartered in Sandefjord, Norway with operations in Izmir, Turkey. We "
"combine patented optical sensor R&D, advanced engineering design, equipment "
"manufacturing, and hands-on fish farming expertise under one roof — giving "
"our clients a single partner for their entire aquaculture journey."
