"sensorer og utstyr på minutter — ingen utskifting. Over den gir en "
"flerleietakerplattform hver leietaker sin egen isolerte database, ubegrenset"
" antall sensorer, mobil drift og vitenskapsbaserte grafer — med AI som "
"hjelper deg å beslutte."

msgid ""
"Suderra Edge runs on our own Suderra OS and plugs into your existing sensors"
" and equipment in minutes — no rip-and-replace. Above it, a secure platform "
"gives every client its own isolated database, unlimited sensors, mobile "
"operations and science-based charts — with AI helping you decide."
