"Suderra includes 24+ preset nutrient recipes for common crops including "
"leafy greens, herbs, tomatoes, peppers, strawberries, and more. You can also"
" create unlimited custom recipes and share them across facilities."
msgstr ""
"Suderra inkluderer 24+ forhåndsinnstilte næringsresepter for vanlige "
