msgstr "Visualisering av Suderra-plattformens dashboard"

msgid ""
"Suderra supports NFT (Nutrient Film Technique), DWC (Deep Water Culture), "
"ebb-and-flow, drip irrigation, vertical farming towers, and aquaponics "
"systems. The platform adapts to any soilless growing method."
msgstr ""
