"flo-og-fjære, dryppvanning, vertikale dyrkingstårn og akvaponikk-systemer. "
"Plattformen tilpasser seg enhver jordløs dyrkingsmetode."

msgid ""
"Suderra supports recirculating aquaculture systems (RAS), flow-through "
"facilities, and open-pen operations. The modular architecture adapts to any "
"setup — from small hatcheries to large-scale salmon farms."
msgstr ""
