"Suderra tracks sea lice count data from your monitoring activities, "
"maintains historical trends per pen and site, and alerts you when counts "
"approach the regulatory threshold. Reports are automatically formatted for "
"Mattilsynet submission."
msgstr ""
"Suderra sporer lusetellingsdata fra overvåkingsaktivitetene dine, "
"vedlikeholder historiske trender per merd og lokalitet, og varsler deg når "
"tellinger nærmer seg den regulatoriske terskelen. Rapporter formateres "
"automatisk for Mattilsynet-innsending."

msgid ""
"Suderra's AI engine uses published scientific formulas and peer-reviewed "
